MessageBox is nothing but simply a pop-up which will appear on screen with ceratin option as:
ok,exit,clean etc

CODE TO DISPLAY INFO:
from tkinter import *
import tkinter.messagebox

root=Tk()

tkinter.messagebox.showinfo("title","this is message")// box with headline title and message will pop-up
response=tkinter.messagebox.askquestion("Question1","Coffe?")
if response=='yes':
    print("here is a coffe for you") //first tkinter messagebox will come after pressing ok question will come
else:
    print("you aint human")
root.mainloop() 
